snippet.title: Reader Rabbit Math Adventures Ages 6–9 - Part 1/6
snippet.description: Reader Rabbit and Sam the lion are stuck in an unknown island while having a boat race. Fortunately, they meet Penelope Parrot who knows everything on this island. The three friends team up together to explore the whole to find boat pieces to assemble a boat to sail back to Wordville, before they will be ambushed by the Pirats who are lurking in this island.
